com.eim.utility.statistics.model
Class ComputedStatistics

java.lang.Object
  com.eim.utility.statistics.model.ComputedStatistics
All Implemented Interfaces:
IStatistics, java.io.Serializable
@Entity
public class ComputedStatistics
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, IStatistics

POJO representing the non-benchmark related statistics.

It is annotated with hibernate annotations for persistence purpose.
These statistics are persisted in the table STATS_COMPUTED and identified using a sequence called SEQ_STATS_COMPUTED. That POJO possesses 5 fields (other than the id field) that are mandatory:

  • targetEntityType
  • targetEntityId
  • applicationDate
  • computationDate
  • status

sdj
